room_description:
Your eccentric uncle Thaddius recently passed away, leaving behind an attic full of mysteries. You have a feeling that a stolen treasure might be hidden among his possessions. Your challenge is to follow the clues he left behind to uncover the fortune and find the truth.

Your team has a choice of how you to play the game, either traditional or modern escape room style.
